---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { getLegalOperator } from "@/config/legal";
import type { Locale } from "@/lib/i18n";
interface Props { locale: Locale; }
const { locale } = Astro.props;
const operator = getLegalOperator();
---
<BaseLayout {locale} title={locale === "de" ? "Datenschutz" : "Privacy"} description={locale === "de" ? "Datenschutzhinweise für Webpilot." : "Webpilot privacy information."}>
  <div class="[&_.legal-page]:mx-auto [&_.legal-page]:min-h-0 [&_.legal-page]:max-w-reading [&_.legal-page]:px-page [&_.legal-page]:pt-36 [&_.legal-page]:pb-30 [&_.legal-page]:text-body [&_.legal-page_.eyebrow]:block [&_.legal-page_.eyebrow]:text-center [&_.legal-page_h1]:mx-auto [&_.legal-page_h1]:mt-8 [&_.legal-page_h1]:mb-16 [&_.legal-page_h1]:block [&_.legal-page_h1]:max-w-[14ch] [&_.legal-page_h1]:text-center [&_.legal-page_h1]:text-display-sm [&_.legal-page_h1]:font-semibold [&_.legal-page_h2]:mt-16 [&_.legal-page_h2]:mb-4 [&_.legal-page_h2]:text-heading-lg [&_.legal-page_h2]:font-semibold [&_.legal-page_p]:text-[#555]">
  <main id="main-content"><article class="legal-page legal-page--standalone"><span class="eyebrow">{locale === "de" ? "Rechtliches" : "Legal"}</span><h1>{locale === "de" ? "Datenschutzhinweise" : "Privacy notice"}</h1>{locale === "de" ? <><h2>Verantwortlicher</h2><p>{operator ? <>{operator.legalName}, {operator.streetAddress}, {operator.postalCode} {operator.city}, {operator.country}, {operator.email}</> : <>Webpilot Studio · <a href="mailto:hello@webpilot.studio">hello@webpilot.studio</a></>}</p><h2>Hosting und technische Protokolle</h2><p>Die Website wird über Cloudflare Workers und statische Assets ausgeliefert. Cloudflare verarbeitet technisch notwendige Verbindungs- und Sicherheitsdaten. Worker-Protokolle enthalten nur Anfrage-ID, Ergebnis, Validierungskategorie, Sprache und gegebenenfalls die Resend-Nachrichten-ID; Formularinhalte werden nicht protokolliert.</p><h2>Kontaktformular</h2><p>Name, E-Mail, optional Unternehmen, Interessen, Projektbeschreibung, Budgetrahmen und Sprache werden zur Beantwortung der Anfrage verarbeitet. Webpilot speichert keine Einreichungen in einer Datenbank. Resend übermittelt die Nachricht per E-Mail. Cloudflare Turnstile prüft die Anfrage auf Missbrauch.</p><h2>Analytics</h2><p>Wenn Cloudflare Web Analytics konfiguriert ist, werden aggregierte Nutzungsdaten ohne Cookies erfasst.</p><h2>Aufbewahrung und Rechte</h2><p>Technische Protokolle werden nur so lange aufbewahrt, wie es für Sicherheit und Fehlerbehebung erforderlich ist. E-Mails werden entsprechend geschäftlicher und gesetzlicher Fristen verwaltet. Anfragen zu Betroffenenrechten richten Sie an <a href="mailto:hello@webpilot.studio">hello@webpilot.studio</a>.</p></> : <><h2>Controller</h2><p>{operator ? <>{operator.legalName}, {operator.streetAddress}, {operator.postalCode} {operator.city}, {operator.country}, {operator.email}</> : <>Webpilot Studio · <a href="mailto:hello@webpilot.studio">hello@webpilot.studio</a></>}</p><h2>Hosting and technical logs</h2><p>The website is served through Cloudflare Workers and static assets. Cloudflare processes technically necessary connection and security data. Worker logs contain only request ID, outcome, validation category, locale, and, where applicable, the Resend message ID; form content is never logged.</p><h2>Contact form</h2><p>Name, email, optional company, interests, project brief, budget range, and locale are processed to answer the enquiry. Webpilot stores no submissions in a database. Resend delivers the message by email. Cloudflare Turnstile checks submissions for abuse.</p><h2>Analytics</h2><p>When Cloudflare Web Analytics is configured, aggregate usage data is collected without cookies.</p><h2>Retention and rights</h2><p>Technical logs are retained only as long as needed for security and troubleshooting. Emails are managed according to applicable business and statutory periods. Send data-subject requests to <a href="mailto:hello@webpilot.studio">hello@webpilot.studio</a>.</p></>}</article></main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
